"""Save the digitized NRV Fig 9A reference data (Couppey et al. 2024) + in-vivo
benchmark (Nannini & Horch 1991 = NH), provided by the user, into
paper_figs/out/data/nrv_reference.json for the validation overlay.

Panel A only: recruitment (norm.) vs current (µA) at 20 / 50 µs — NH dots + NRV
curves. (The pulse-width sweep / 7-8-9 µA series was dropped — that benchmark
probes the long-pulse rheobase, which a coarse mesh under-resolves for an
intrafascicular wire, and its digitized PW axis was ambiguous.)
"""
